hopobject.body: A company car docetaxel cytoxan breast cancer And, as if further to deny his reputation as a “hawk”, Mr Weale insists that further quantitative easing remains very much a tool at the Bank of England’s disposal. He admits that he was sceptical about whether the first round of QE had been as effective as claimed, and he agrees there have been some negative consequences. Even so, more QE must remain an option should the economy need further support beyond the “forward guidance” just offered, he insists.
